                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@Paul: And maybe the same attitude will lead to him being hit by a bus when he fails to look both ways before crossing the street, but you haven&apos;t warned him about that. Edit: I had thought you were the poster of this answer, my mistake.&lt;/span&gt;

