            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;How many bytes an INT(1) takes is product specific, and also what INT(1) means. Can be one digit, one byte, one word, or perhaps something else?&lt;/span&gt;

